<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="celebration-n">celebration <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌselɪ'breɪʃn/    美 /ˌselɪ'breɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 庆祝活动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>birthday / wedding celebrations</strong> 
生日/结婚庆典</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>hold / have a celebration 
举行庆祝活动</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] [常用单数] 庆祝；歌颂：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>in celebration of</strong> one’s promotion
庆祝某人升职</p></div></div>